(7, 1, '2014-12-10 18:45:51', '2014-12-10 10:45:51', '静夜思\r\n床前明月光\r\n\r\nsdf \r\nTwee Tonx whatever, Godard Marfa Truffaut flannel cliche heirloom freegan. Godard umami cardigan next level. Deep v paleo banjo kitsch gentrify wolf. IPhone craft beer Carles, tofu plaid post-ironic street art pickled American Apparel stumptown dreamcatcher crucifix. You probably haven’t heard of them bicycle rights retro, actually aesthetic kitsch Carles YOLO sartorial. Banh mi Williamsburg narwhal mumblecore, Tonx vegan small batch. Meh PBR&B Helvetica fanny pack Intelligentsia, organic vegan freegan pop-up Etsy master cleanse gastropub brunch street art.\r\n\r\nPost-ironic asymmetrical Brooklyn tattooed. Gastropub swag salvia direct trade. Brooklyn forage authentic, iPhone actually seitan small batch polaroid Williamsburg raw denim Tonx meggings Truffaut Echo Park jean shorts. Lo-fi keytar butcher, Wes Anderson iPhone crucifix freegan normcore Godard +1 twee cliche vinyl Intelligentsia. Typewriter flannel fap, slow-carb Helvetica Carles blog food truck cred swag meh Blue Bottle put a bird on it. Put a bird on it beard organic, mustache quinoa gluten-free food truck pug authentic lo-fi messenger bag drinking vinegar. Pitchfork deep v VHS, flexitarian Echo Park Portland normcore Brooklyn semiotics meh irony DIY.', '测试文章', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%b5%8b%e8%af%95%e6%96%87%e7%ab%a0', '', '', '2014-12-10 18:45:51', '2014-12-10 10:45:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost/menpai/cargroup/?p=7', 0, 'post', '', 0),
