(1, 1, '2014-11-10 08:54:21', '2014-11-10 08:54:21', '欢迎使用WordPress。这是系统自动生成的演示文章。编辑或者删除它，然后开始您的博客！', '世界，你好！', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2014-11-10 08:54:21', '2014-11-10 08:54:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/menpai/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(2, 1, '2014-11-10 08:54:21', '2014-11-10 08:54:21', '这是示范页面。页面和博客文章不同，它的位置是固定的，通常会在站点导航栏显示。很多用户都创建一个“关于”页面，向访客介绍自己。例如，个人博客通常有类似这样的介绍：\n\n<blockquote>欢迎！我白天是个邮递员，晚上就是个有抱负的演员。这是我的博客。我住在天朝的帝都，有条叫做杰克的狗。</blockquote>\n\n……公司博客可以这样写：\n\n<blockquote>XYZ Doohickey公司成立于1971年，自从建立以来，我们一直向社会贡献着优秀doohicky。我们的公司总部位于天朝魔都，有着超过两千名员工，对魔都政府税收有着巨大贡献。</blockquote>\n\n您可以访问<a href="http://localhost/menpai/wp-admin/">仪表盘</a>，删除本页面，然后添加您自己的内容。祝您使用愉快！', '示例页面', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2014-11-10 08:54:21', '2014-11-10 08:54:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/menpai/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(4, 1, '2014-11-10 18:18:07', '2014-11-10 10:18:07', '<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	Flannel next level hella Shoreditch. Seitan fashion axe Marfa DIY, skateboard yr fanny pack 90’s squid Intelligentsia roof party sustainable asymmetrical church-key. Truffaut Echo Park lomo bespoke, selvage sriracha Banksy beard post-ironic crucifix dreamcatcher ennui keytar shabby chic. Locavore forage wayfarers jean shorts trust fund fanny pack. Ethical farm-to-table biodiesel Vice Thundercats 90’s craft beer kogi next level. Chia keffiyeh fixie, XOXO meggings organic scenester gluten-free cred swag Helvetica. Seitan hoodie Echo Park Thundercats, deep v authentic Godard semiotics.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	Twee Tonx whatever, Godard Marfa Truffaut flannel cliche heirloom freegan. Godard umami cardigan next level. Deep v paleo banjo kitsch gentrify wolf. IPhone craft beer Carles, tofu plaid post-ironic street art pickled American Apparel stumptown dreamcatcher crucifix. You probably haven’t heard of them bicycle rights retro, actually aesthetic kitsch Carles YOLO sartorial. Banh mi Williamsburg narwhal mumblecore, Tonx vegan small batch. Meh PBR&amp;B Helvetica fanny pack Intelligentsia, organic vegan freegan pop-up Etsy master cleanse gastropub brunch street art.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	Post-ironic asymmetrical Brooklyn tattooed. Gastropub swag salvia direct trade. Brooklyn forage authentic, iPhone actually seitan small batch polaroid Williamsburg raw denim Tonx meggings Truffaut Echo Park jean shorts. Lo-fi keytar butcher, Wes Anderson iPhone crucifix freegan normcore Godard +1 twee cliche vinyl Intelligentsia. Typewriter flannel fap, slow-carb Helvetica Carles blog food truck cred swag meh Blue Bottle put a bird on it. Put a bird on it beard organic, mustache quinoa gluten-free food truck pug authentic lo-fi messenger bag drinking vinegar. Pitchfork deep v VHS, flexitarian Echo Park Portland normcore Brooklyn semiotics meh irony DIY.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	Blue Bottle Williamsburg iPhone Cosby sweater, ugh trust fund art party fingerstache fixie mlkshk kale chips Truffaut cliche +1 flannel. Farm-to-table lomo yr, skateboard hoodie kogi twee keytar cardigan selvage slow-carb narwhal Wes Anderson. High Life ethical stumptown 3 wolf moon, tote bag slow-carb Portland. 8-bit viral forage, cray Godard gastropub banjo readymade butcher Carles bespoke semiotics. Shoreditch blog meggings VHS, roof party Kickstarter four loko salvia raw denim quinoa swag sriracha skateboard. Paleo Etsy church-key High Life, direct trade meh meggings wolf synth salvia Pinterest. Butcher Marfa 8-bit Godard bespoke.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	Meggings fap put a bird on it, keytar authentic photo booth ethical Thundercats mumblecore Odd Future viral vegan. Tonx ennui slow-carb bicycle rights, beard readymade YOLO butcher. Heirloom cardigan Echo Park, squid post-ironic semiotics sriracha retro. Master cleanse polaroid Tonx, fixie 90’s locavore quinoa farm-to-table cliche occupy fingerstache. Chillwave Carles kale chips, Kickstarter skateboard letterpress biodiesel XOXO aesthetic sustainable tattooed Cosby sweater crucifix trust fund kogi. Tilde gluten-free squid letterpress, Williamsburg American Apparel keytar. Small batch next level stumptown tote bag yr, banh mi tousled 3 wolf moon McSweeney’s leggings irony PBR&amp;B narwhal.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	Vegan Intelligentsia Pinterest tilde. Vice try-hard small batch Etsy Tumblr, Godard 90’s fashion axe 8-bit lomo. Locavore yr four loko, skateboard sustainable selfies irony cred Neutra readymade scenester Vice Bushwick. Vinyl cred messenger bag pop-up, Godard umami fingerstache. Tonx Carles asymmetrical stumptown beard, pickled food truck Austin Thundercats pour-over selvage tofu small batch. Meggings whatever High Life, freegan fashion axe Bushwick keytar. Mumblecore butcher retro farm-to-table iPhone raw denim, ennui PBR hella mlkshk vegan Blue Bottle dreamcatcher.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<iframe src="http://localhost/menpai/wp-content/plugins/kindeditor-for-wordpress/plugins/baidumap/index.html?center=118.796911%2C32.051025&amp;zoom=19&amp;width=558&amp;height=360&amp;markers=118.796911%2C32.051025&amp;markerStyles=l%2CA" frameborder="0" style="width:560px;height:362px;">\r\n	</iframe>\r\n</p>', 'Chia keffiyeh fixie, XOXO meggings organic scenester gluten-free cred swag', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ckfxmosgfcs', '', '', '2014-11-19 14:51:59', '2014-11-19 06:51:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/menpai/?p=4', 0, 'post', '', 0),
